description:
Danny does his very first Everything Iconic Live episode from The Troubadour in LA, with special guests Ariana Madix and Tom Sandoval from Vanderpump Rules. They talk about the next season, SUR rumors, Fancy AF Cocktails, and more! Hannah Brown (host of Brown-Eyed Jewnicorn) also joins Danny to talk OC and Dallas Housewives! Special thanks to all of you who showed up! The show will be back to regularly scheduled recaps after next week.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
